  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the this study was to compare the safety and efficacy of HalfLytely (2L
      NULYTELY + 20mg bisacodyl) to NULYTELY for preparation prior to colonoscopy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
